description: Austin, Bryan, and Eli just got home from watching a movie, discussing their opinions and whatnot. Somewhere during the conversation, Bryan utters the words ‘banana peel’, which sends Austin into a submissive trance. Eli and Bryan have been studying subliminal ques and apparently, it worked on Austin, as he was down on his knees taking off their shoes immediately. Bryan orders him to massage their feet, but Austin takes things even further by sucking on their socked and bare feet until they’ve both been fully foot worshipped!
title: Eli and Bryan Foot Worshiped by Austin
